Etogolong'aka enkaiguanani Fashiti olaiguanani Serser


1   Ore apa too nkolong'i e Serser, Serser laa ninye apa oitore ebaiki India ometabaiki Etiopia, ilkerenketi oobaya iip o tikitam oopishana. 
2  Ore te nena olong'i ina kata pee eton olaiguanani Serser to lorika lenye le nkitoo te Susa, naa ninye enkang kitok. 
3  Ore to lari liokuni le nkitoria enye neitobiraki osirua ilkituaak lenyena, o sinkan, Netii sii ilkituaak le njore le Parsia o Media o larikok o laiguanak loo lkerenketi dukuya ninye, 
4  ina kata eitoduaya enkarsisisho e nkitoo enye e nkisisa, o enkishiaa e nkitoo enye too nkolong'i kumok. Inkolong'i iip o ntomoni isiet. 
5  Ore ake pee ebaya nena olong'i, neisho olaiguanani lelo tung'ana pooki ootii Susa, ina ang kitok, ilkituaak o looti osirua too nkolong'i naapishana, ti atua enkaji e ntumo natii atua olgoriet le nkurma e ina manyisho o laiguanani. 
6  Netii ilkarash ooibor o lpusi ooika eisiong'are iusin sidain naanyokie olgiso le nkosholai o ng'apeta naashetuno too soito oowang, netii sii ilorikan dapashi le sahabu o enkosholai shumata oleng'oti loo soito oonyokie o loonyori, netii isoito oogol enkinyang'a. 
7  Neisho ninche metookisho too nkikompeni e sahabu oo mpukunot kumok, naa eisapuk oleng enaisho oo sabibu anaa enaikununo enkaminino o laiguanani. 
8  Ore eokore naa anaa enaitanapishoteki, mearakini hoo ng'ae, amu eitanapishe olaiguanani too lkituaak lenyena pooki ootii enkaji enye e nkitoo nchere nchoo metaasa pooki tung'ani enayieu. 
9  Neisho sii Fashiti ina kitok o laiguanani inkituaak o sirua te ina aji e nkitoo o laiguanani Serser.


10  Ore te nkolong' e naapishana, etishipe oltau lo laiguanani te nkaraki enaisho oo sabibu, neitanap ninye Mehuman, o Bista, o Harbona, o Bigta, o Abaguta o Setar o Karkas, lelo sunaishi oogelema oopishana ooisiaisho te dukuya olaiguanani Serser, 
11  pee eyau Fashiti dukuya olaiguanani eishopito emaupe enye e nkitoo pee eitodol iltung'ana pooki o lkituaak pooki e nkishiaa enye, amu eisidai apa oleng te nking'urata. 
12  Kake etanya apa Fashiti ina kitok o laiguanani, elotu te ina kitanapata o laiguanani anaa enatolimutuo lelo sunaishi oogelema. Neitagor ina olaiguanani oleng, netiu engoro enye anaa enkima nayupuyup ti atua ninye.


13  Nejoki olaiguanani ilang'eni ooyiolo nkatitin, amu ilo apa olkerreti lo laiguanani ti alo lelo pooki arriyiak too nkitanapat o te nkiguana. 
14  Ore apa iltung'ana ootashare ninye naa Karshena o Shetar, o Admata, o Tarshish, o Meres, o Marsena, o Memukan, lelo kituaak oopishana le Parsia o Media, ootoduaa enkomom o laiguanani, naa ninche ootang'asa aatoni te nkitoo enye. 
15  Nejoki, “Amaa te risioroto oo nkitanapat kaa eitaasi Fashiti amu eitu eas enaitanapa olaiguanani Serser natolikitio lelo sunaishi oogelema?” 
16  Nejoki Memukan te dukuya olaiguanani o lelo kituaak, “Mme ake olaiguanani eitaasa Fashiti entorrono, kake eitaasa sii ilkituaak pooki o ltung'ana pooki ootii iloshon pooki lo laiguanani Serser. 
17  Amu ore ena yasata e ina kitok o laiguanani naa keyiolou nkituaak pooki, nemenu ilpayiani lenye, te neimakini aajo eitanapishe olaiguanani Serser ajo meyauni Fashiti dukuya enye, neany elotu. 
18  Ore ninye taata ena olong ntomonok e Parsia o Media naaidipa aatoning olkuak le nkitok o laiguanani naa keliki ilkituaak pooki lo laiguanani, neaku sapuk olmena o engoro. 
19  Tenaa keitiship ena olaiguanani, nchoo epukunye ninye enkitanapata, neigeri too nkitanapat oo Lpasia o Lmedia pee meibelekenyi, nchere meitoki ae kata Fashiti alotu dukuya Serser, naa nchoo eisho olaiguanani erishata enye e nkitoo esupat alang ninye. 
20  Ore ake pee einosuni aaibalunye ina kitanapata o laiguanani ti atua enkitoo enye pooki, aa sapuk anaa enatiu, pee eisho nkituaak enkanyit ilpayiani lenye, lkituaak o looti.” 
21  Neitiship ena utaroto olaiguanani, o lkituaak, neas olaiguanani anaa enatolimuo Memukan. 
22  Neirriwaa mpala iloshon pooki le nkitoria enye, olosho ake too lkigeroto lenye o te nkutuk enkiroroto enye, nchere pee eaku olee ake ninye pooki olaitoriani le nkaji enye, neiro te risioroto enkutuk o lorere lenye.

